{"tid":745384,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[減肥Post] 個人已經唔靚仔，如果變埋肥仔就中晒肥矮毒柒窮。","createTime":"2018-07-16T16:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T10:43:45.000Z","uid":1941,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"46bca70c022d0e4afa1ab47e3ece248e60690675","tid":745384,"uid":1941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:49:34.000Z","msg":"冇錯，我就係中晒肥矮毒柒窮五宗罪嗰個肥仔。先講下背景<br />\n<br />\n21歲，身高夠拎傷殘津貼得174cm，體重80KG。<br />\n<br />\n以BMI計法，差少少就到輕度肥胖，以前做開運動既我開始接受唔到身型就黎變個波咁。<br />\n<br />\n開個Post除左想記錄下減肥經歷，同時想屌柒一班想不勞而獲想靠食減肥藥或者節食既柒頭，知唔知你地咁做短期係會瘦左，但係長期一定會反彈啊傻西。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>Day 1: Falt Tire</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先講下今日既飲食，同平時差唔多唔想點樣節食，但係必會做既野係<strong>多飲水</strong>同埋<strong>戒食宵夜</strong>。晏就食左一個南記小窩米線/凍奶茶，晚餐就有一碗白飯/泡菜/蕃茄炒蛋/Somersby 350ml。<br />\n<br />\n講返做運動方面，睇左我起底就知我係一個單車仔黎，所以今日本身想踩訓練台既帶氧訓練黎打底，打算慢慢加強返訓練強度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/003329_d78a22c4da34c941fb1f5b97b2b0b0cd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F003329_d78a22c4da34c941fb1f5b97b2b0b0cd.png&h=7461abad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所謂既訓練台其實姐係單車機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，個人就對住部電腦咁踩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/003254_a72cd2c7a06bfb7536d6c8bcdcf1277d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F003254_a72cd2c7a06bfb7536d6c8bcdcf1277d.png&h=ec4fea14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知踩左30分鐘左右Hang左機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是我就換左衫落街踩街，踩到咁上下點碌返屋企既時候發覺左，點解條頭呔好似淋淋地咁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n落車一睇，仆街爆左呔，差少少返到屋企都要上的士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n七月十六日小計：41Km。<br />\n<br />\n體重就唔會日日磅住，咁快輕左可能係身體流失既水份黎，咁快磅冇意義。<br />\n<br />\n聽日應該唔會踩車住，可能轉一轉跑步先。"},{"pid":"1cb8a29623f2e010ffd1b833001cab5935a31347","tid":745384,"uid":96308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:55:13.000Z","msg":"少糖，野飲最好少甜/走甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油"},{"pid":"25445f5d4d3043c35f4c6808746d179bc8f0851b","tid":745384,"uid":113371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:56:13.000Z","msg":"我都成80幾kg又好懶唔想做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbd0151ce99cac0385954e3778a9a02636b1d7b","tid":745384,"uid":127804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:59:08.000Z","msg":"亞洲人黎講 80kg 好似已經中度肥胖 醫管局有得計"},{"pid":"56f8c828343d2b54d40acca13978eb8b9ed87e60","tid":745384,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:58:52.000Z","msg":"自爆?"},{"pid":"0b54cc21170fc65577fa12b4b9179827cfbbbdb7","tid":745384,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:07:20.000Z","msg":"174叫矮我170係咪要自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff68209650adb733164a0b7904ac6cd847abf748","tid":745384,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b54cc21170fc65577fa12b4b9179827cfbbbdb7","tid":745384,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:07:20.000Z","msg":"174叫矮我170係咪要自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:39:49.000Z","msg":"我165<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c760cd79f674e9a9bfb236dcceb66d89b359e204","tid":745384,"uid":1941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b54cc21170fc65577fa12b4b9179827cfbbbdb7","tid":745384,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:07:20.000Z","msg":"174叫矮我170係咪要自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:42:01.000Z","msg":"一齊拎傷殘津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95ad911a27c044e2332bfe34fe642a76a63412d","tid":745384,"uid":1941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:43:45.000Z","msg":"七月十七.<br />\n<br />\n出面熱到仆街，踩左一個鐘頭機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/184302_e5b5fd85ba3e1854d18d3be0b3669026.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F184302_e5b5fd85ba3e1854d18d3be0b3669026.png&h=7017293b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做完運動記得拉筋，今日好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}